content.description:
Start by climbing a short, arching crack (the same as

Fertile Crescent

) to an obvious jug where the crack becomes horizontal. From here, launch into a sea of 5.12 slab and face climbing to an obvious undercling rest at 3/4's height. A long, 6 to 8 move, crux sequence takes you past the last 2 bolts before you exit left to the crack, and follow that to the anchor.
